	 <a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/09/enabling-extension-updates/" style="text-decoration:none;" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link: Enabling Extension Updates">
	 Enabling Extension Updates</a>
    </h3>


	         <div class="post-body">
	<div>
      	<p>So you&#8217;ve learned how to <a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2004/12/08/how-to-create-firefox-extensions/">write your own extension</a>. This tutorial will show you how to keep your users up to date with your latest version automatically.</p>

<p><a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/09/enabling-extension-updates/#more-20">Read the rest of this entry &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="post-footer">
      <em>posted by Eric on <a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/09/enabling-extension-updates/">03.09.05</a> @ 5:16 pm</em> | <a class="comment-link" href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/09/enabling-extension-updates/#comments"><em><a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/09/enabling-extension-updates/#comments">15 Comments</a></em></a>
    </p>
  

  </div>



  <div class="post">
    <h3 class="post-title">
	 <a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/08/alphabetical-hack-in-place/" style="text-decoration:none;" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link: Alphabetical hack in place">
	 Alphabetical hack in place</a>
    </h3>


	         <div class="post-body">
	<div>
      	<p>I finally figured out how to hack the categories to display in alphabetical order. The archives are untouched, so if for some reason you wanted to see them in chronological order, you can. If anyone else wanted to know how to do this, you modify the wp-includes/classes.php file. Go to line 462, and add in this:</p>

<pre>
// Alphabetical hack for categories
if ($whichcat)
    {
        $q['orderby'] = 'title';
        $q['order'] = 'ASC';
    }
</pre>
    </div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="post-footer">
      <em>posted by Eric on <a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/08/alphabetical-hack-in-place/">03.08.05</a> @ 3:33 pm</em> | <a class="comment-link" href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/08/alphabetical-hack-in-place/#comments"><em><a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/08/alphabetical-hack-in-place/#comments">2 Comments</a></em></a>
    </p>
  

  </div>



  <div class="post">
    <h3 class="post-title">
	 <a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/06/ext2abc/" style="text-decoration:none;" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link: Ext2Abc">
	 Ext2Abc</a>
    </h3>


	         <div class="post-body">
	<div>
      	<p>Adds a &#8220;Sort&#8221; button on the extension manager to arrange your extensions alphabetically. There&#8217;s no permanent change to the order, as this had a possibility of corrupting the extension manager&#8217;s files.</p>

<p>
<a href="http://extensions.roachfiend.com/ext2abc.xpi">Install Ext2Abc 0.2.1</a><br />
<small>(<b>Size</b>: <i>12kb</i> <b>Release Date</b>: <i>September 24th 2004</i>)</small><br/>
<i><small>Tested on Firefox 0.9 - 0.10.</small></i>
</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="post-footer">
      <em>posted by Eric on <a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/06/ext2abc/">03.06.05</a> @ 3:55 pm</em> | <a class="comment-link" href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/06/ext2abc/#comments"><em><a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/06/ext2abc/#comments">9 Comments</a></em></a>
    </p>
  

  </div>



  <div class="post">
    <h3 class="post-title">
	 <a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/06/teleflip/" style="text-decoration:none;" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link: Teleflip">
	 Teleflip</a>
    </h3>


	         <div class="post-body">
	<div>
      	<p>Send instant messages to cell phones via Firefox. It uses the free service <a href="http://www.teleflip.com/">Teleflip</a> and the freeware <acronym title="Simple Mail Transfer Protocol">SMTP</acronym> mailer <a href="http://www.blat.net">Blat</a>. Currently only compatibile with Windows and service areas of North America.</p>

<p>
<a href="http://extensions.roachfiend.com/teleflip.xpi">Install Teleflip 0.1.1</a><br />
<small>(<b>Size</b>: <i>37kb</i> <b>Release Date</b>: <i>September 2nd 2004</i>)</small><br/>
<i><small>  Tested on Firefox 0.9 - 0.10.</small></i>
</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="post-footer">
      <em>posted by Eric on <a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/06/teleflip/">03.06.05</a> @ 3:53 pm</em> | <a class="comment-link" href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/06/teleflip/#comments"><em><a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/06/teleflip/#comments">6 Comments</a></em></a>
    </p>
  

