  <div class="post">
    <h3 class="post-title">
	 <a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/03/word-count/" style="text-decoration:none;" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link: Word Count">
	 Word Count</a>
    </h3>


	         <div class="post-body">
	<div>
      	<p>Will count the number of words in any text that is selected. Simply highlight the text, right-click,
and select &#8220;Word Count&#8221;. A pop-up window will show you how many words are in that selection.</p>

<p>
<a href="http://extensions.roachfiend.com/wordcount.xpi">Install Word Count 0.1.1</a><br />
<small>(<b>Size</b>: <i>8kb</i> <b>Release Date</b>: <i>August 10th 2004</i>)</small><br/>
<i><small>  Tested on Firebird 0.7, Firefox 0.8 - 0.10, Mozilla 1.6, 1.7b and Netscape 7.1.</small></i>
</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="post-footer">
      <em>posted by Eric on <a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/03/word-count/">03.03.05</a> @ 11:26 am</em> | <a class="comment-link" href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/03/word-count/#comments"><em><a href="http://roachfiend.com/archives/2005/03/03/word-count/#comments">4 Comments</a></em></a>
